at the conclusion of God's tribute song to

01:08:19.729 --> 01:08:20.510
his beloved son.

01:08:21.630 --> 01:08:23.451
It would already be the most important

01:08:24.770 --> 01:08:26.270
piece of literature ever written,

01:08:27.311 --> 01:08:30.511
a very constitution of our lives,

01:08:30.652 --> 01:08:32.752
an owner's manual, if you will,

01:08:33.092 --> 01:08:35.274
an operator's manual on how to get the

01:08:35.333 --> 01:08:36.613
most out of life.

01:08:36.634 --> 01:08:44.115
Just a quick interruption here.

01:08:45.131 --> 01:08:47.972
There has been a really nasty bug that

01:08:48.012 --> 01:08:50.573
has permeated this island.

01:08:50.913 --> 01:08:51.875
One of my closest friends,

01:08:51.895 --> 01:08:52.734
he showed up today.

01:08:52.774 --> 01:08:55.435
He works with us four days a week,

01:08:57.277 --> 01:08:58.037
an artist friend.

01:08:58.078 --> 01:08:59.177
He's really a talented fellow.

01:09:01.537 --> 01:09:03.219
He has been waylaid with it for two

01:09:03.238 --> 01:09:03.659
weeks now.

01:09:05.039 --> 01:09:07.881
And it starts with a sinus infection,

01:09:08.202 --> 01:09:09.342
which I'm subject to,

01:09:09.903 --> 01:09:11.024
and then a scratchy throat,

01:09:11.043 --> 01:09:12.425
which you probably heard me cough over

01:09:12.484 --> 01:09:15.466
these last two weeks, more so than normal.

01:09:16.067 --> 01:09:18.787
And then it just renders you too weak

01:09:18.828 --> 01:09:22.130
to be productive for two to three weeks.

01:09:22.871 --> 01:09:26.113
And so I'm trying to avoid mind

01:09:26.153 --> 01:09:27.753
progressing to what his did.

01:09:28.333 --> 01:09:29.033
So for a while,

01:09:29.054 --> 01:09:31.395
we're just going to do the one program

01:09:31.895 --> 01:09:32.275
a week,

01:09:32.855 --> 01:09:34.695
and I'm going to get lots and lots

01:09:34.737 --> 01:09:37.837
of rest and drink lots of fluids to

01:09:37.957 --> 01:09:40.738
try to minimize the likelihood that it

01:09:41.458 --> 01:09:45.440
waylays me at this time.

01:09:45.501 --> 01:09:51.823
So, what God has just articulated.

01:09:55.154 --> 01:09:58.036
by way of the relationship between yada

01:09:58.076 --> 01:10:00.037
and dot,

01:10:00.057 --> 01:10:03.820
between the sun and the moon symbolically,

01:10:04.501 --> 01:10:06.542
the greater and lesser luminaries from

01:10:06.762 --> 01:10:07.844
God's perspective,

01:10:09.104 --> 01:10:10.746
the tree of lives and the tree of

01:10:10.805 --> 01:10:13.507
knowledge, the ram and bull,

01:10:15.729 --> 01:10:17.690
the king and Obed-Edom.

01:10:20.734 --> 01:10:22.175
All of this is going to be accomplished.

01:10:23.814 --> 01:10:24.413
It's going to take root.

01:10:24.434 --> 01:10:25.034
It's going to grow.

01:10:25.055 --> 01:10:28.778
It's going to yield an eternal harvest.

01:10:28.818 --> 01:10:29.738
Our king will endure.

01:10:29.939 --> 01:10:32.159
He will return.

01:10:32.381 --> 01:10:33.100
His offspring,

01:10:33.121 --> 01:10:36.103
the children of the covenant, will thrive.

01:10:37.384 --> 01:10:38.824
And he will never serve alone.

01:10:40.327 --> 01:10:42.448
He will always have his herald.

01:10:47.032 --> 01:10:49.774
The son's dignity, his authority,

01:10:51.029 --> 01:10:53.292
as well as his symbols of majesty,

01:10:53.332 --> 01:10:56.194
will be as brilliant as the sun in

01:10:56.234 --> 01:10:57.293
his father's presence.

01:10:58.295 --> 01:11:00.617
Adorned in the vestiges of his calling,

01:11:02.217 --> 01:11:05.020
Dowd will become Yahowah's most conspicuous

01:11:05.159 --> 01:11:05.859
counterpart.

01:11:07.822 --> 01:11:11.283
I said something on our vlog on the

01:11:11.323 --> 01:11:13.765
vlog last Sunday,

01:11:14.886 --> 01:11:19.989
that while I have been amazingly impressed

01:11:21.140 --> 01:11:24.502
with the renditions of Dowd and all of

01:11:24.542 --> 01:11:26.662
our branding and outreach material that

01:11:26.703 --> 01:11:29.503
have been produced by my wife and her

01:11:29.543 --> 01:11:33.645
team of exceedingly artistic and creative

01:11:33.685 --> 01:11:34.385
individuals.

01:11:35.286 --> 01:11:38.506
But there was one that was not as

01:11:39.606 --> 01:11:41.648
Dowdian as I wanted it to be.

01:11:42.228 --> 01:11:44.128
And I guess it was a collaborative effort

01:11:44.248 --> 01:11:47.470
between my wife and a really remarkable

01:11:48.310 --> 01:11:50.350
young man that is super,

01:11:51.088 --> 01:11:56.572
devoted to helping us convey this message,

01:11:56.851 --> 01:11:58.533
particularly on Facebook,

01:11:58.573 --> 01:12:00.073
where he is really active.

01:12:00.953 --> 01:12:02.975
And he has one of the great life

01:12:03.036 --> 01:12:05.056
stories of having fallen and gotten back

01:12:05.157 --> 01:12:05.317
up.

01:12:05.837 --> 01:12:08.398
But my understanding is he was one that

01:12:08.438 --> 01:12:09.319
created that image.

01:12:12.847 --> 01:12:16.208
I am, by design, exceedingly judgmental,

01:12:16.788 --> 01:12:19.890
and I am also, by design, very vocal.

01:12:20.550 --> 01:12:22.690
God made me this way for this purpose.

01:12:23.110 --> 01:12:23.810
And I said, you know,

01:12:23.850 --> 01:12:25.070
of all the things that we've done,

01:12:25.570 --> 01:12:27.051
I think we could make that dote a

01:12:27.112 --> 01:12:27.952
bit more regal.

01:12:29.872 --> 01:12:31.972
And the reason I said that is because

01:12:32.012 --> 01:12:33.153
of statements like this.

01:12:33.193 --> 01:12:33.953
He's returning,

01:12:34.353 --> 01:12:36.293
and he's as brilliant as the sun.

01:12:36.354 --> 01:12:38.453
He is Elyown in God's presence.

01:12:38.774 --> 01:12:40.255
He is the greater luminary son.

01:12:41.175 --> 01:12:46.756
I want my king to appear as God's

01:12:47.815 --> 01:12:49.155
conspicuous counterpart.

01:12:49.195 --> 01:12:49.936
And my wife,

01:12:50.716 --> 01:12:53.497
she is the most talented fashion designer

01:12:53.676 --> 01:12:54.436
I have ever met.

01:12:54.697 --> 01:12:54.856
Now,

01:12:54.896 --> 01:12:56.078
you wouldn't know it by the way that

01:12:56.217 --> 01:12:56.658
I dress,

01:12:56.698 --> 01:12:58.717
but we're pretty casual around here.

01:12:59.198 --> 01:13:01.319
But she is really stylish.

01:13:01.378 --> 01:13:04.259
And so I just wanted Dowd to be

01:13:04.578 --> 01:13:08.119
as God sees him, as I see him,

01:13:08.500 --> 01:13:09.220
as we see him.

01:13:11.788 --> 01:13:12.948
Now, speaking of the two,

01:13:13.048 --> 01:13:15.630
just speaking of God's metaphor, the moon,

01:13:16.149 --> 01:13:18.250
while four hundred times smaller than the

01:13:18.369 --> 01:13:18.609
sun,

01:13:18.689 --> 01:13:21.390
is four hundred times closer to the earth.

01:13:22.411 --> 01:13:24.311
And that's four hundred times smaller in

01:13:25.612 --> 01:13:26.391
diameter.

01:13:27.532 --> 01:13:30.132
Much, much smaller than the sun than that,

01:13:30.172 --> 01:13:31.632
but just in diameter.

01:13:33.252 --> 01:13:34.253
And the moon,

01:13:35.134 --> 01:13:37.134
comprised of the essence of the earth,

01:13:37.373 --> 01:13:40.335
actually our moon was created because of

01:13:40.875 --> 01:13:40.895
a...

01:13:41.476 --> 01:13:44.498
of a very large planet, smaller,

01:13:44.599 --> 01:13:47.220
of course, than the Earth,

01:13:47.282 --> 01:13:49.603
but probably in the size of Mars,

01:13:51.645 --> 01:13:53.065
four and a half billion years ago,

01:13:53.565 --> 01:13:55.387
hit Earth at just the proper speed and

01:13:55.427 --> 01:13:58.869
just the proper angle to fuse with the

01:13:58.970 --> 01:14:01.671
Earth and send an enormous amount of the

01:14:01.773 --> 01:14:04.073
Earth out into orbit around the Earth as

01:14:04.555 --> 01:14:04.835
the moon.

01:14:05.555 --> 01:14:06.815
And so the...

01:14:09.395 --> 01:14:11.378
Moon is comprised of the same material of

01:14:11.399 --> 01:14:11.800
the Earth.

01:14:12.520 --> 01:14:15.828
And it is illuminated as a result of

01:14:15.868 --> 01:14:17.270
reflecting the sun's light.

01:14:17.994 --> 01:14:18.354
Boy,

01:14:18.636 --> 01:14:22.198
it's been gorgeous these last few mornings

01:14:22.618 --> 01:14:26.823
as you see a full moon in the

01:14:26.922 --> 01:14:28.425
pre-dawn hours.

01:14:29.365 --> 01:14:31.868
Even as the sun begins to rise in

01:14:31.908 --> 01:14:34.850
the west, the moon is just brilliant.

01:14:35.270 --> 01:14:36.572
And I think it's Saturn that's been

01:14:36.612 --> 01:14:39.395
dangling below it all of this time.

01:14:39.454 --> 01:14:41.516
It's just a marvelous sight.

01:14:42.884 --> 01:14:44.505
So it's now we're actually seeing a full

01:14:44.524 --> 01:14:46.987
moon during the early daylight hours, too,

01:14:47.167 --> 01:14:49.609
as we approach this conclusion of time.

01:14:50.389 --> 01:14:52.411
So these two, the sun and the moon,

01:14:52.430 --> 01:14:54.372
they serve as metaphors to portray the

01:14:54.532 --> 01:14:58.194
proper perspective to view all that God

01:14:58.234 --> 01:15:01.436
has fulfilled through the Mowedym by

01:15:01.476 --> 01:15:04.720
describing him as the second most

01:15:04.779 --> 01:15:07.601
important luminary compared to his father.

01:15:08.662 --> 01:15:09.143
But the

01:15:09.818 --> 01:15:12.979
greater luminary compared to other men and

01:15:13.020 --> 01:15:16.962
to myself as the lesser luminary god is

01:15:17.442 --> 01:15:20.064
conveying to us that Down's arrivals are

01:15:20.123 --> 01:15:24.105
important markers in time and that by by

01:15:24.365 --> 01:15:27.967
using the sun to mark years and the

01:15:28.068 --> 01:15:31.449
moon to mark months we know the timing

01:15:31.569 --> 01:15:32.871
not only of the

01:15:33.371 --> 01:15:35.673
fulfillment of the Mowedym as the

01:15:35.694 --> 01:15:36.755
fourteenth, fifteenth,

01:15:36.814 --> 01:15:38.877
and sixteenth day of the first month,

01:15:39.436 --> 01:15:40.859
as seven sevens,

01:15:40.899 --> 01:15:43.640
or forty-nine days from the heart of

01:15:43.822 --> 01:15:46.003
Matsah to Shabuwah,

01:15:46.543 --> 01:15:50.448
and then the Taruwah

01:15:51.256 --> 01:15:53.837
Kipurym and Sukah on the first day of

01:15:53.877 --> 01:15:54.798
the seventh month,

01:15:55.338 --> 01:15:57.581
the tenth and the fifteenth day of that

01:15:57.661 --> 01:15:57.961
month.

01:15:58.740 --> 01:16:02.703
These are all times that are associated

01:16:02.743 --> 01:16:05.265
with our place in the earth's orbit around

01:16:05.305 --> 01:16:08.306
the sun and the phases of the moon.

01:16:10.047 --> 01:16:12.988
So they are markers of the Mowedym and

01:16:13.009 --> 01:16:18.152
they are the very men that fulfill them.

01:16:18.171 --> 01:16:19.533
So the seven Mowedym.

01:16:21.158 --> 01:16:21.978
are fulfilled through them.

01:16:23.979 --> 01:16:27.621
And we are enlightened as a result of

01:16:27.640 --> 01:16:27.761
them.

01:16:29.601 --> 01:16:30.943
And it was in the fullness of the

01:16:30.983 --> 01:16:34.543
moon's light also that Dowd fulfilled

01:16:34.583 --> 01:16:35.545
Pesach and Matsah.

01:16:36.805 --> 01:16:38.565
It's always a full moon during Pesach and

01:16:38.586 --> 01:16:38.945
Matsah.

01:16:39.407 --> 01:16:41.427
It's always a full moon when we return

01:16:42.448 --> 01:16:44.649
on Sukah to the garden.

01:16:46.069 --> 01:16:48.770
It is interesting that when Dowd fulfilled

01:16:49.731 --> 01:16:50.252
Pesach,

01:16:51.670 --> 01:16:54.150
and Matsah in thirty three CE.

01:16:55.551 --> 01:16:59.613
There was a full lunar eclipse.

01:17:02.615 --> 01:17:07.497
When Yahowah brings us back into the garden

01:17:07.918 --> 01:17:10.159
on Sukah in twenty thirty three.

01:17:12.440 --> 01:17:13.442
On October seventh.

01:17:15.101 --> 01:17:17.823
There will be a full lunar eclipse.

01:17:21.029 --> 01:17:24.372
On the day of Pesach Matsah Bikuwrym in

01:17:24.412 --> 01:17:25.412
thirty three C.E.

01:17:25.431 --> 01:17:27.092
that sets up this final year,

01:17:27.552 --> 01:17:30.335
there will be a full lunar eclipse.

01:17:33.617 --> 01:17:35.117
And on Taruwah,

01:17:36.637 --> 01:17:39.219
which is when the lesser luminary as the

01:17:39.279 --> 01:17:43.822
moon serves his king by laying down his

01:17:43.902 --> 01:17:44.681
Basar body,

01:17:44.742 --> 01:17:46.582
his life as the Adam of Parah,

01:17:46.783 --> 01:17:48.963
his man from Edom to save this mortal

01:17:49.003 --> 01:17:49.965
remnant of Yisrael.

01:17:51.502 --> 01:17:56.685
there will be a full solar eclipse it's

01:17:56.765 --> 01:18:00.087
the one time only one time where the

01:18:00.127 --> 01:18:05.891
moon is actually possessed placed in a

01:18:05.931 --> 01:18:09.175
position that's more important than the

01:18:09.234 --> 01:18:12.817
sun just for that day and that's the

01:18:12.856 --> 01:18:17.961
day that yada as the king's herald lays

01:18:18.001 --> 01:18:19.082
down his life as

01:18:20.454 --> 01:18:21.194
the man from Edom,

01:18:22.015 --> 01:18:23.256
and the Adam of Parah.

01:18:26.938 --> 01:18:28.019
It's a pretty interesting story,

01:18:28.059 --> 01:18:29.800
the way it's all woven together, isn't it?

01:18:31.081 --> 01:18:32.881
All so that we can be part of

01:18:32.942 --> 01:18:33.782
Yahowah's family.

01:18:36.023 --> 01:18:36.203
So,

01:18:36.622 --> 01:18:39.145
while Dowd is Yahowah's most enduring and

01:18:39.204 --> 01:18:41.765
reliable witness, he has a herald,

01:18:42.326 --> 01:18:42.787
a Basar.

01:18:44.314 --> 01:18:45.054
Basar, of course,

01:18:45.475 --> 01:18:47.215
is also synonymous with body,

01:18:47.274 --> 01:18:52.777
and it was his body that fulfilled Pesach,

01:18:53.117 --> 01:18:55.597
and it is my body that will fulfill

01:18:55.637 --> 01:18:56.078
Taruwah.

01:18:57.618 --> 01:18:59.319
But the primary meaning of the word is

01:18:59.378 --> 01:19:02.640
derived from its verbal root,

01:19:03.280 --> 01:19:05.081
which is to be a herald,

01:19:05.100 --> 01:19:08.181
to convey information that's important.

01:19:09.203 --> 01:19:11.243
And ed means restoring a witness.

01:19:11.262 --> 01:19:13.264
That's why it's the Mow'ed.

01:19:15.469 --> 01:19:18.291
to ponder the implications of the

01:19:18.331 --> 01:19:19.712
restoring witness to the eternal

01:19:19.771 --> 01:19:20.353
testimony.

01:19:21.594 --> 01:19:23.255
These are the roles that we play together.

01:19:24.315 --> 01:19:27.979
It is why the lesser luminary is the

01:19:28.880 --> 01:19:32.382
tree of the knowledge of good and evil.

01:19:33.162 --> 01:19:35.225
It is why when the Choter is presented,

01:19:36.945 --> 01:19:39.148
that he is shown as a branch.

01:19:39.889 --> 01:19:43.872
He is called an observant branch,

01:19:44.452 --> 01:19:44.953
a Netzar.

01:19:46.177 --> 01:19:47.479
It is said of him that he has

01:19:47.559 --> 01:19:47.979
roots.

01:19:49.399 --> 01:19:52.520
It is said that he is parah, fruitful,

01:19:52.860 --> 01:19:55.023
Adamah parah, that he is fruitful.

01:19:55.682 --> 01:19:57.323
And it says that he has the spirit

01:19:57.363 --> 01:19:58.203
of both etzah,

01:19:58.684 --> 01:20:00.145
which is the counsel of that tree,

01:20:01.326 --> 01:20:03.827
and Da'ath, of the seven spirits.

01:20:04.327 --> 01:20:05.507
Da'ath is the sixth.

01:20:06.688 --> 01:20:09.550
It is the etzah of Da'ath,

01:20:09.569 --> 01:20:10.510
the tree of knowledge,

01:20:11.591 --> 01:20:13.431
about the tree of lives.

01:20:16.618 --> 01:20:17.639
This is God's message.

01:20:18.880 --> 01:20:19.520
It's powerful.

01:20:20.141 --> 01:20:20.822
It's irrefutable.

01:20:22.583 --> 01:20:24.826
It's infinitely superior to the lie of

01:20:24.886 --> 01:20:27.047
Jesus or of Allah or of Hashem.

01:20:28.689 --> 01:20:30.752
It destroys the religions of Christianity,

01:20:31.453 --> 01:20:32.573
Islam, and Judaism,

01:20:33.595 --> 01:20:35.657
and it replaces them with the most

01:20:35.877 --> 01:20:37.759
profoundly important, most beautiful,

01:20:37.838 --> 01:20:39.279
most enlightening and uplifting

01:20:40.774 --> 01:20:43.775
message that god has ever offered those

01:20:44.355 --> 01:20:47.837
who listen and capitalize on what father

01:20:47.877 --> 01:20:51.979
and son have achieved so I thank you

01:20:52.100 --> 01:20:53.621
for listening I hope it has been a

01:20:53.661 --> 01:20:56.302
beautiful day as we've tried to capture so

01:20:56.342 --> 01:21:00.324
much of the elegance and light these long

01:21:00.404 --> 01:21:03.426
shadows in this late afternoon over our

01:21:03.466 --> 01:21:07.048
beautiful garden of an island

01:21:08.207 --> 01:21:10.717
and the shimmering sea behind.

01:21:11.903 --> 01:21:13.149
May you have a wonderful rest of your

01:21:13.168 --> 01:21:13.289
day.